<DOCNO> AP880819-0047 </DOCNO>
<FILEID>AP-NR-08-19-88 0445EDT</FILEID>
<1ST_LINE>r a PM-People-Emmys     08-19 0116</1ST_LINE>
<2ND_LINE>PM-People-Emmys,0119</2ND_LINE>
<HEAD>Mary Tyler Moore, Dick Van Dyke Tapped for Emmy Duty</HEAD>
