<HEAD>With PM-Vincennes Report</HEAD>
<HEAD>Reagan Briefed, Concurs with Report</HEAD>
<DATELINE>SANTA BARBARA, Calif. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   President Reagan concurs in the
actions taken by Secretary of Defense Frank C. Carlucci on the
Navy's report on the downing of an Iranian airliner by the USS
Vincennes, the president's spokesman said today.
   Marlin Fitzwater, in Santa Barbara while the president vacations
