the current session of the U.N. Subcommission on the Prevention of
Discrimination and Protection of Minorities.
   Romanian officials advised the panel that Mazilu would be unable
to attend due to a heart condition. They said he had left Bucharest
to undergo treatment at an unspecified resort.
